OL,3,CToddler home for Christmas after life-
OL,4,Csaving heart transplant
OL,6,FA toddler who endured a year-long wait
OL,7,Fin hospital for a new heart has
OL,8,Freturned home for Christmas after a
OL,9,Flife-saving transplant.
OL,11,FPenelope Greathead, from Whitby in
OL,12,FNorth Yorkshire, suffered a life-
OL,13,Fthreatening cardiac arrest in November
OL,14,F2024 after being born with a condition
OL,15,Fcalled dilated cardiomyopathy.
OL,17,FThe now two-year-old has spent the
OL,18,Flast year at London's Great Ormand
OL,19,FStreet Hospital being kept alive by a
OL,20,Fmachine known as a "Berlin Heart",
OL,21,Fwhich does the work of an organ.
