OL,3,CToddler home for Christmas after life-
OL,4,Csaving heart transplant
OL,6,FAnd in October her parents received
OL,7,Fthe news that a donor had been found.
OL,9,FSpeaking for the first time since the
OL,10,Fsuccessful operation, Penelope's mum,
OL,11,FHolly Suff, said: "Obviously, we had
OL,12,Fbeen waiting for such a long time that
OL,13,Fyou want it to happen but at the same
OL,14,Ftime it's just so nerve-wracking
OL,15,Fbecause it's such a major operation.
OL,17,F"There's still nothing right about
OL,18,Fhanding your little girl over to
OL,19,Fsurgeons who are going to do something
OL,20,Flike that."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
