OL,4,Csaving heart transplant
OL,6,FHolly and her partner Jordan Greathead
OL,7,Fmoved to London for the duration of
OL,8,FPenelope's stay in hospital and
OL,9,Fwelcomed their second daughter,
OL,10,FBeatrice, in April.
OL,12,FPenelope had to remain connected to
OL,13,Fmedical equipment when the family took
OL,14,Ftrips out.
OL,16,FFollowing the transplant, Penelope
OL,17,Fremained in a coma for two days with
OL,18,Fher chest open in case surgeons needed
OL,19,Fto re-operate.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
