OL,4,Csaving heart transplant
OL,6,FBut a few days later she was up and
OL,7,Fmoving, and a few weeks later she was
OL,8,Fback home in Whitby.
OL,10,FJordan said: "When it got to about 10
OL,11,Fmonths (in hospital), a part of me
OL,12,Fstarted to think we were never going
OL,13,Fto leave and just be in London and in
OL,14,Fthat hospital setting forever.
OL,16,F"She loved her little farm animal
OL,17,F(toys) the whole time we were in
OL,18,Fhospital. I think she just thought
OL,19,Fthey were little 3D creatures, but now
OL,20,Ffor her to be able to see them all out
OL,21,Fof her bedroom window is fantastic."
