OL,6,FThe family's joy has been tempered by
OL,7,Fthe knowledge that Penelope's new
OL,8,Fheart came thanks to a heart donation
OL,9,Ffrom another child who had died.
OL,11,FHolly said: "It's hard because that
OL,12,Ffamily now haven't got their little
OL,13,Fperson at home for Christmas, so it's
OL,14,Ftough.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
