OL,3,CToddler home for Christmas after life-
OL,4,Csaving heart transplant
OL,6,F"The morning after (Penelope's)
OL,7,Fsurgery it had been crazy stormy
OL,8,Fweather and we woke up in the morning
OL,9,Fand it was a beautiful, sunny, crisp
OL,10,Fday. I just thought that little person
OL,11,Fis looking down on us and hoping
OL,12,Feverything goes alright.
OL,14,F"We've just got to have them in our
OL,15,Fthoughts and let them know we'll give
OL,16,Fher the best life possible and we will
OL,17,Fcherish the gift they gave us."
